  "detailed_description": "Guide Major Tom through amazing Sci-fi settings, an explosion of colors and shapes inspired by the Space Age and Science Fiction of all time. With an evocative original soundtrack that will immerse you in the visual universe of Astrodelia.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Test your ability to solve puzzles and brain teasers. Outwit enemies, overcome obstacles and mazes, think outside the box in order to save the Solar System from a terrible wandering black hole.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is also a parallel <i>“Easter Egg”</i> type challenge, for those who want to go further, consisting of the search for hidden codes in some scenes of the game through the interpretation of an ancient prophecy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>More than 30 surprising scenarios ensure hours of fun in this captivating sidereal graphic adventure. Pure fantasy.",
  "about_the_game": "Guide Major Tom through amazing Sci-fi settings, an explosion of colors and shapes inspired by the Space Age and Science Fiction of all time. With an evocative original soundtrack that will immerse you in the visual universe of Astrodelia.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8447a2fc35caa0f48e24fbfcc2694388.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Test your ability to solve puzzles and brain teasers. Outwit enemies, overcome obstacles and mazes, think outside the box in order to save the Solar System from a terrible wandering black hole.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/8e01226fba60dc7bbe909a918d1c5ec3.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is also a parallel <i>“Easter Egg”</i> type challenge, for those who want to go further, consisting of the search for hidden codes in some scenes of the game through the interpretation of an ancient prophecy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.poster.avif?t=1720108976\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.webm?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775550/extras/aa918417cb92c7d082f5c8234af9fe1b.mp4?t=1720108976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>More than 30 surprising scenarios ensure hours of fun in this captivating sidereal graphic adventure. Pure fantasy.",
